{"tid":864021,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"得巨乳得天下 巨乳聚人心　「松鼠奶」讓日本鄉民瘋狂了","createTime":"2018-10-16T02:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T03:05:15.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"417b223372951395f65c45050fed4c800db19165","tid":864021,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:43:22.000Z","msg":"最近日本人為了一張「巨乳照」而瘋狂，再次應證了「巨乳聚人心」的效應。<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，這張巨乳照的主角不是別人，就是一隻松鼠。日本一名推特網友「@boblim1204」表示，本月初他到東京井之頭自然文化園遊玩，意外拍到這隻「大奶松鼠」，不少網友直呼，這根本像極迪士尼卡通《奇奇蒂蒂》的女性角色克莉絲(Clarice)。<br />\n<br />\n這張照片一出籠，立刻吸引14萬推特網友按「喜歡」，還被轉推了4.6萬次。網友們也紛紛直呼：「未來松鼠就進化了！」、「要做胸罩嗎？」、「我原本以為是P圖，但看起來好像是真的。」另外也有網友認為，到了10月中之後，松鼠會進入冬眠，所以在此之前，牠們會把自己吃得肥肥的。<br />\n井之頭自然文化園當中有著名的松鼠小徑，民眾可以近距離觀察到松鼠生態，園區官方推特也不時會分享松鼠門的可愛動態。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181016/1448277\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181016%2F1448277&d=5%2FstAs133giDQ%2FmLdZaAAcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d94bb640\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181016%2F1448277&h=11c12cf7\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181016/1448277</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181016/640_e878157917cb0802722c4db090d45c0b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181016%2F640_e878157917cb0802722c4db090d45c0b.jpg&h=876e35d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181016/640_967457eb8ef300a6c2dd13e230a0d227.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181016%2F640_967457eb8ef300a6c2dd13e230a0d227.jpg&h=b5026087&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔: 今天唔j miss了"},{"pid":"6ad3aa01a3a220250684f96cfc7f0c470f9ef770","tid":864021,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"第一張隻松鼠有冇得養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a934e152108c2f483fba442867d42a5ece389a90","tid":864021,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6ad3aa01a3a220250684f96cfc7f0c470f9ef770","tid":864021,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"第一張隻松鼠有冇得養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T02:46:49.000Z","msg":"第一張好似係龍貓 香港無嘅"},{"pid":"49b3b9c3263d5210a50ba4c6b474be52b1964ba6","tid":864021,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"俾日本仔見到好快就有H 圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}